<div class="title">Breakthrough in Technology (DMT Made Easy)</div>
<div class="substance">DMT & 5-MeO-DMT</div>
<div class="author">by <A HREF="exp.cgi?A=ShowAuthor&ID=282">Teafaerie</A></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Teaf&aelig;rie. "Breakthrough in Technology (DMT Made Easy): An Experience with DMT & 5-MeO-DMT (exp66957)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 9, 2007. erowid.org/exp/66957</div>

<br/>



